"pay, year-end bonuses (as per sectoral or other collective labor "
"agreements), benefits in kind and their estimated value"
msgstr ""
"Salaire fixe ou horaire, rémunération variable, primes, titres-repas, éco-"
"chèques, pécule de vacances (y compris pécule de vacances anticipé le cas "
"échéant), indemnités de rupture, primes de fin d'année (conformément aux "
"conventions collectives sectorielles ou autres), avantages en nature et leur "
"valeur estimée"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1860
msgid "Gross amount of all remuneration components"
msgstr "Montant brut de tous les éléments de rémunération"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1861
